### ===========================================
### Simple API Test File
### ===========================================
### Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code
### Click "Send Request" above each request
### ===========================================

### Get all products
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products

### Get one product (replace ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE

### Create product
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "price": 999,
  "category": "electronics"
}

### Create another product
POST http://localhost:3000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Phone",
  "price": 699,
  "category": "electronics"
}

### Update product (replace ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop",
  "price": 1299
}

### Delete product (replace ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
